The '''Crumpled Namelist''' is an interactable that can be found inside [[Jeht]]'s tent in the [[Tanit Camps]].

==Text==
(This is a simple list of names. Apart from "Masseira," all the other names have been struck out.)<br>
[[Bleda]]<br>
[[Gwaffah]]<br>
[[Izder]]<br>
[[Meddur]]<br>
[[Teyya]]<br>
[[Masseira]]

==Lore==
The list consists of names of members of the [[Tanit]] tribe. From the context of the conversations that Jeht has with the [[Traveler]] and [[Babel]] in the {{Quest|For Her Judgment Reaches to the Skies...}}, it can be inferred that it is a "hit list" of people Babel ordered Jeht to assassinate. After Jeht leaves the Tanit, the list disappears from her tent, and can be found again in a tent in the canyon past [[Liloupar's Cell]], below [[Wadi Al-Majuj]]'s western [[Teleport Waypoint]].
